General.Name: WinVest Acquisition Corp. Warrant
General.Description: WinVest Acquisition Corp. intends to effect a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to focus its search on target businesses in the financial services industry with a focus on financial media, brokerage, banking, investing, and wealth management. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Cambridge, Massachusetts.
